{"data":{"page":{"html":"<h1 id=\"client-server-information-and-api-entry-point\"><a href=\"#client-server-information-and-api-entry-point\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Client: server information and API entry point</h1>\n<div class=\"toc\">\n<h2><a href=\"#toc\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Table of Contents</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#creating-a-new-client\">Creating a new client</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#grab-an-instance-of-hbaseclient\">Grab an instance of \"hbase.Client\"</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#events\">Events</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#api-version\">API: version</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#api-version_cluster\">API: version_cluster</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#api-clientstatus_cluster\">API: client.status_cluster</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#api-clienttables\">API: client.tables</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#api-clienttable\">API: client.table</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"creating-a-new-client\"><a href=\"#creating-a-new-client\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Creating a new client</h2>\n<p>A new instance of \"HBase\" may be instantiated with an object containing the following properties:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">protocol</code> (string, optional, default to \"localhost\")<br>\nOne of 'http' or 'https', default to \"http\".</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">host</code> (string, required)<br>\nDomain or IP of the HBase Stargate server.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">port</code> (string|int, optional, default to \"8080\")<br>\nPort of the HBase REST server.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">krb5</code> (object, required for secure connection)<br>\nConfiguration object for Kerberos.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">krb5.principal</code> (string, required for secure connection)<br>\nKerberos user principal.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">krb5.password</code> (string, optional)<br>\nKerberos password of the user principal or null if using a keytab or the default credential cache.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">krb5.keytab</code> (string, optional)<br>\nPath to the Kerberos keytab or null if using a password or the default credential cache.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">krb5.service_principal</code> (string, required for secure connections)\nGSS service principal in the form of \"HTTP@{fqdn}\", automatically discovered if \"host\" is a correct FQDN.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">timeout</code> (int, optional)<br>\nNumber of milliseconds before the request timeout.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Other custom options that can be passed to requests. For possible options, take a look at <a href=\"https://nodejs.org/api/http.html#http_http_request_options_callback\">http</a> or <a href=\"https://nodejs.org/api/https.html#https_https_request_options_callback\">https</a> request.</p>\n<h2 id=\"grab-an-instance-of-hbaseclient\"><a href=\"#grab-an-instance-of-hbaseclient\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Grab an instance of \"hbase.Client\"</h2>\n<p>Calling the <code class=\"language-text\">hbase</code> method return an initialized client object.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> hbase <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'hbase'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> client <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">hbase</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> options <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>You can also manually construct a new instance as follow:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> hbase <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'hbase'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> client <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">hbase<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Client</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> options <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"events\"><a href=\"#events\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Events</h2>\n<p>The client extends the native Node.js <a href=\"https://nodejs.org/api/events.html\">EventEmitter API</a>. The following events are emitted:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">request</code><br>\nAn object with the keys <code class=\"language-text\">options</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">data</code> if the request is of type \"PUT\" or \"POST\".</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"api-version\"><a href=\"#api-version\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>API: version</h2>\n<p>Query Software Version.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">client<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">version</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>error<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> version<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">info</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>version<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Will print something similar to:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Server\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"jetty/6.1.24\"</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"REST\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"0.0.2\"</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"OS\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Mac OS X 10.6.4 x86_64\"</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Jersey\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"1.1.5.1\"</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"JVM\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Apple Inc. 1.6.0_20-16.3-b01-279\"</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"api-version_cluster\"><a href=\"#api-version_cluster\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>API: version_cluster</h2>\n<p>Query the storage cluster version.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">client<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">version_cluster</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> error<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> version <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">info</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> version <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Will print something similar to:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"csv\"><pre class=\"language-csv\"><code class=\"language-csv\">&#39;0.89.20100726&#39;</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"api-clientstatus_cluster\"><a href=\"#api-clientstatus_cluster\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>API: client.status_cluster</h2>\n<p>Query the storage cluster status.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">client<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">status_cluster</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> error<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> statusCluster <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">info</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> statusCluster <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Will print something similar to:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"requests\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"regions\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"averageLoad\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"DeadNodes\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">null</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"LiveNodes\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> Node<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>Object<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"api-clienttables\"><a href=\"#api-clienttables\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>API: client.tables</h2>\n<p>List of all non-system tables.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">client<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">tables</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>error<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> tables<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">info</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>tables<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Will print something similar to:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token property\">\"name\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"node_hbase\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"api-clienttable\"><a href=\"#api-clienttable\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>API: client.table</h2>\n<p>Return a new instance of <a href=\"./table.md\">\"hbase.Table\"</a> and get access to a table. From there, multiple operations are available to create, modify and delete HBase tables as well as to access rows and scanners.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Client","description":"Retrieve server information and API entry point","keywords":"hbase, client, server information, version, status, cluster, tables, namespaces"},"fields":{"edit_url":"https://github.com/adaltas/node-hbase-docs/edit/master/src/md/api/client.md"}}},"pageContext":{}}